<li><cite id="Smith"><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFD.M_Smith.2C_T.W._Goodwin.2C_J.A.Schiller">D.M Smith, T.W. Goodwin, J.A.Schiller (pdf). <i><a href="http://www.airproducts.com/NR/rdonlyres/E44F8293-1CEE-4D80-86EA-F9815927BE7E/0/ChallengestoHeliumSupply111003.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.airproducts.com/NR/rdonlyres/E44F8293-1CEE-4D80-86EA-F9815927BE7E/0/ChallengestoHeliumSupply111003.pdf" rel="nofollow">CHALLENGES TO THE WORLDWIDE SUPPLY OF HELIUM IN THE NEXT DECADE</a></i>. Air Products and Chemicals, Inc<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.airproducts.com/NR/rdonlyres/E44F8293-1CEE-4D80-86EA-F9815927BE7E/0/ChallengestoHeliumSupply111003.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.airproducts.com/NR/rdonlyres/E44F8293-1CEE-4D80-86EA-F9815927BE7E/0/ChallengestoHeliumSupply111003.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.airproducts.com/NR/rdonlyres/E44F8293-1CEE-4D80-86EA-F9815927BE7E/0/ChallengestoHeliumSupply111003.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-07-01</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=CHALLENGES+TO+THE+WORLDWIDE+SUPPLY+OF+HELIUM+IN+THE+NEXT+DECADE&amp;rft.aulast=D.M+Smith%2C+T.W.+Goodwin%2C+J.A.Schiller&amp;rft.au=D.M+Smith%2C+T.W.+Goodwin%2C+J.A.Schiller&amp;rft.pub=Air+Products+and+Chemicals%2C+Inc&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.airproducts.com%2FNR%2Frdonlyres%2FE44F8293-1CEE-4D80-86EA-F9815927BE7E%2F0%2FChallengestoHeliumSupply111003.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Helium-3"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></cite></li>
